XOF setup: alg=0 (invalid)
xof_setup_fail:0:PSA_ERROR_INVALID_ARGUMENT

XOF setup: alg=category (invalid)
xof_setup_fail:PSA_ALG_CATEGORY_XOF:PSA_ERROR_NOT_SUPPORTED

XOF setup: alg=SHA3-256 (invalid)
xof_setup_fail:PSA_ALG_SHA3_256:PSA_ERROR_INVALID_ARGUMENT

XOF setup: alg=SHAKE128 not supported
depends_on:!PSA_WANT_ALG_SHAKE128
xof_setup_fail:PSA_ALG_SHAKE128:PSA_ERROR_NOT_SUPPORTED

XOF states: inactive
xof_state_inactive:

XOF set_context: SHAKE128 (bad)
depends_on:PSA_WANT_ALG_SHAKE128
xof_state_set_context:PSA_ALG_SHAKE128:PSA_ERROR_BAD_STATE

XOF state: SHAKE128 without set_context (good)
depends_on:PSA_WANT_ALG_SHAKE128
xof_state_good_context:PSA_ALG_SHAKE128:0

XOF state: SHAKE128 late set_context (bad)
depends_on:PSA_WANT_ALG_SHAKE128
xof_state_late_context:PSA_ALG_SHAKE128:0

XOF skip update = update(0): SHAKE128
depends_on:PSA_WANT_ALG_SHAKE128
xof_state_skip_update:PSA_ALG_SHAKE128:0
